1-121.Certified public accountant; fees; when payable.

The applicable fee shall be paid by the applicant at the time he or she applies for examination or reexamination.

SourceLaws 1957, c. 1, § 16, p. 60;Laws 1991, LB 75, § 10;Laws 1997, LB 114, § 18;Laws 2016, LB853, § 4.
